prompt.title: Embedding for Creating AI Apps with Promptbook
prompt.content: Promptbook is a new framework for building AI applications using a human-readable markup language called "Book."  It supports various large language models (LLMs) including OpenAI's o3-mini, DeepSeek models, and offers integrations with other APIs like Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini, and Azure OpenAI.
